post.content:
Dear Band Families,

Hope you all are doing well. The Spring Band Banquet is on May 2nd. Please consider volunteering for this event. More information will be coming soon but we wanted to give you a heads up due to how busy the Spring always gets. Have a great day! Please contact us if you have any questions.

Sincerely,

Hospitality Committee
Amy Schultz, Kristen Coffman, Carrie Barnett and Kathy Payne

May Band Banquet
